Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:02.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NORTH BLUE - 16 YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:07.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SPIDER MILES - A PORT TOWN\NTHE WASTE PROCESSING PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.60,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,A BOY FROM THE WHITE TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:18.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,TRAFALGAR LAW (10 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to eat-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That crazy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy wants to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no mercy, Corazon.\NYou hate kids so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll kill him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next target is Rakesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools from that town \Nwag their tails at us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhile allying with other groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them pay for their betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? We're having dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's fine.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I called him.\N--You did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:06:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Law! It's been a week now.\NDon't you wanna get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been getting beaten by Corazon\Nsince you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids run away and so do adults.\NThat's why we only have the best here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer\Nwill a powerless brat like you last?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget the "Blood Law"\Nno matter how you get harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Family will fall apart\Nif a member defies us Executives' authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once laughed at Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Nand almost died from torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can bluff as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Corazon is my precious,\Nbiological, younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone so much as cuts him once,\NI will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...put them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's White Lead Disease!\NIt's agonizing pain if you get infected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's contagious?!\NYou're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here now-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giolla, don't spread information\Nwhich is nothing more than a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Buffalo believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Lead Disease come from poisoning.\NIt's not contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But stay away from me just in case-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI don't wanna catch such a disease-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other survivors\Nin the White Town, Flevance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NI was just desperate to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I crossed the border\Nhiding under a stack of dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you holding grudge against?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in anything anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon! Don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get my revenge on you\Nat any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you stupid?\NWeren't you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll torture you if you do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NImpalement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think their apologetic tears\Nwill guarantee forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,RAKESH - A PORT TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Don Quixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armsmorphosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-Ton Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what kind of place is the White Town\Nwhere that kid was from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People called the whole land Flevance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Flevance?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens were all rich
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the towns were all white, \Nfrom the soil to the plants,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nlike a snow country in a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the country was out of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, they discovered White Lead,\Na type of lead, underground
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and found out that was the source of\Nthe fantastic scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made utensils, paint,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sweeteners, cosmetics,\Nand even weapons out of White Lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People all over the world wanted to buy\Ntheir high-quality White Lead goods
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it became Flevance's major industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The quick-eyed World Government went into
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the transport business \Nto ship that merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Lead made people a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:53.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FLEVANCE - THE WHITE TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, for this kind of surgery,\Nyou use this blood vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!\NYou're a genius, Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NLet's go to the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm studying now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No! No! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, studying is good but if you push
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yourself too much,\Nit's not good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you need to\Ngo out and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nyou're always working, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea! Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0},\Nlet's go to the festival together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Why don't you three go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. But just for 30 minutes.\NWe have so many patients to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! Let's go! To the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The White Town was\Nthe land everyone longed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanna go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lon"g"ed for! There's the "G"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About a century ago, when the White \NLead industry was established,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government performed\Ngeological survey in the country
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact is they had \Nalready known the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was poison.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison that was not so harmful\Nunless you dig it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you handle it somehow,\Nit'll erode your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erode?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison will harm your body\Njust by touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing this but blinded by\Nthe easy fortune to be had,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Government and the royalty \Nof that country kept it secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens kept digging up White Lead\Nknowing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they did so, they would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the terrible part was\Nit only contained traces of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, the Lead keeps building up\Nin a young person's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he has a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the child will, actually,\Nhave a shorter life expectancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the kid grows up\Nand has his own child
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that child's life expectancy is\Neven shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:54.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NEGATIVE EFFECT\NON FUTURE GENERATIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life expectancy got shorter\Ngeneration by generation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually, a generation doomed to die
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbefore adulthood, just like Law, was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the world finally realized\NWhite Lead is poisonous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! This way! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lammy, you don't have to rush like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the festival ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't end yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lammy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Lammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, people started \Nto collapse one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandparents, parents,\Nand then children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the differences in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their life expectancies,\Nall generations fell ill around the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their skin and hair got whiter rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and people died one after another\Nwith their entire bodies in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doctor could stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all the people in his country died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The real tragedy began after that.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing the people in the White Town\Nall dying with the same symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people in the neighboring countries
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthought White Lead Disease was contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they blocked off the country completely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took quarantine measures\Nagainst the White Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The royalty got help
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Government and escaped \Nthe country at an early stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People from the White Town who \Nwere looking to get treated and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...immigrate to other countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were feared as if they were\Nmonsters escaping from the cage and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they were shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really "swept it under the rug."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain of the disease was\Njust somebody else's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very human like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Flevance couldn't keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironically, they had tons of lead bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, a war broke out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other countries justified their actions \Nas self defense so they showed no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can imagine the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\NCome on, you gotta come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are gentle soldiers who told us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthey will let only the children escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Law!\N--We'll be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! My young sister is dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lammy-{\i1}chan{\i0} is?! I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's ask them to get you \Non board the next ship to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! Aren't you coming?!\NLet's escape together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll save Lammy later, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both my father and mother are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they told me to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna live no matter what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Law-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is always hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A merciful helping hand will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...reach to you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible! I can't go there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough doctors!\NSame for blood and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a way to clear \Naway White Lead from bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not contagious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't the Government report that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-{\i1}sama{\i0}, my body hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My skin's getting whiter and whiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on for a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father is the greatest \Ndoctor in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe'll heal you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so noisy outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival.\NFlevance is always prosperous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get well soon and\Nlet's go to a festival together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for White Lead Disease \Npatients and kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lammy, stay in here for a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got rid of two infected people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law! Let's go! To the festival!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Law-kun.\NThere is always hope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A merciful helping hand will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...reach to you like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's escape together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'm gonna live no matter what!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hospital...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lammy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flevance, the White Town, perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By people's hands, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a ten-year-old kid went \Nthrough such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it screws up his personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There he is! Corazon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My parents, young sister,\Nand everybody from the church were dead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that idiot is alive - it's not fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They won't know if I keep quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody cares...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.87,0:22:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...if a scumbag goes missing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn! He saw!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... b-broke the... Blood Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He deserves impalement-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must inform...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Young Master-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doflamingo was born as one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragons who rule \Neverything in the world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did he lose his noble status?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Doflamingo's unimaginable \Npast is revealed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law's life as a child changes in a big way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A Celestial Dragon! Doffy's Stormy Past!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
